{"article_id":"Xqkyiaoty6BbJmYH","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Another day , another breathless report","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that Vice President Joe Biden is about to announce","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"whether he ' s running for president .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"The latest , from NBC News , has \" two sources \" saying","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that Mr. Biden will let us know by Wednesday morning .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"But we ' ve heard this before","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"- 11 times , in fact ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"and still no decision .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"So don ' t hold your breath .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Sooner or later , though , Biden will end the suspense .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"Some signs point to a run .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"CNN reports","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that Biden associates are \" setting up interviews for potential staff positions \" on a presidential campaign .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Biden is also reportedly meeting with top political advisers Monday night .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"The latest poll on the Democratic primary race , by CNN/ORC , shows Biden at 18 percent , well below Hillary Clinton","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"( 45 percent )","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"and Bernie Sanders","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"( 29 percent ) .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"One can look Biden ' s share two ways :","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Either he ' s doing well for someone","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"who hasn ' t announced","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"or , obviously , campaigned .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Or he ' s doing not so well","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"- third place , for the sitting vice president .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"\" I ' m not sure","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"if a hypothetical number like that really tells you much , \"","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"says Karlyn Bowman , an expert on polling at the American Enterprise Institute in Washington .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"As a noncandidate , Biden hasn ' t made the case for himself as the next president .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"But he also hasn ' t gone through the gauntlet of a campaign","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"- the attacks , the dredging up of the past , the close media scrutiny .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"\" When someone becomes a real-life candidate ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"things really change , \"","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"Ms . Bowman said .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"\" Will we hear stories about his ability","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"to connect with white males , something","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that Hillary has struggled with ?","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Will there be a sympathy factor \" over the death of his son ?","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"Other poll metrics may give Biden more clues to his viability as a potential candidate , such as his favorability scores .","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"Biden is the best-liked of the Democratic candidates ,","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"with 51 percent of Americans seeing him positively","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"versus 37 percent negative .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Clinton scores 46 percent positive , 50 percent negative .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"Sanders is 41-29 .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"In head-to-head matchups against Republican front-runners , Biden does the best of any Democratic candidate .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"He beats Donald Trump by 10 percentage points ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"while Clinton beats him by only 5 points and Sanders by 9 .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Against Ben Carson , Biden also does best :","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"The vice president beats the retired neurosurgeon by 8 points ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"while Clinton and Sanders are in a virtual tie with the doctor .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"( Clinton scores 47 percent to Dr. Carson ' s 48 ;","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Sanders gets 46 percent to Carson ' s 48 . )","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"But again , these matchups are hypothetical .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"There ' s nothing like being a declared candidate","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"that really tests a man","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"( or a woman )","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"seeking the highest office .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"You ' re never more popular than the day","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"before you announce","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"and the day","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"after you get out of the race ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"the saying goes .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"Biden wins kudos now for his \" authenticity , \" that quality of genuineness , of \" Joe being Joe , \"","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"that makes him appealing to many Democrats .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"But the moment","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"he announces ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"if he does ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"the media will be on \" gaffe watch , \"","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"looking for anything","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"he says or does","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"that is out-of-step with Obama administration policy or polite discourse .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"It may , in fact , already be too late .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"As Biden himself declared in August 2003 ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"after deciding not to run in the 2004 race ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"\" You just can ' t parachute into a presidential campaign . \"","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"But even with that in mind ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"Biden confidant Ted Kaufman is telling former staffers to stay in close contact ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"according to an e-mail","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"obtained by the Associated Press .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"`` If he runs ,","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"he will run","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"because of his burning conviction","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"that we need to fundamentally change the balance in our economy and the political structure","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"to restore the ability of the middle class","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"to get ahead , ''","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"said Mr. Kaufman .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":88,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":89,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":90,"text":"Another sign","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"that there may be room","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"for Biden to get in","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"comes from an analysis of Clinton ' s donors .","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"Fewer than 10 percent of the 833 people","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"who raised money for the 2012 Obama-Biden campaign","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"have signed on to \" bundle \" donations for Clinton ,","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"according to USA Today .","depth":5},{"id":98,"text":"Ultimately , Biden ' s decision could come down to his gut .","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"As he has said many times ,","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"he ' s not sure","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"he has the emotional energy","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"to run .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"Soon we will get his final answer .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":207,"left":188,"right":206,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":188,"left":140,"right":187,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":140,"left":113,"right":139,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":112,"right":9,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":106,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":0,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":111,"left":107,"right":110,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"}